      "value": {
        "latex": "Résoudre dans $\\Nn*$ l'équation $\\binom{n}{1}+\\binom{n}{2}+\\binom{n}{3}= 5n$.",
        "html": "<p>Résoudre dans <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Nn*\\)</span> l’équation <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\binom{n}{1}+\\binom{n}{2}+\\binom{n}{3}= 5n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2534f3ef-4c55-4f36-b7b6-5193f29dc05a",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Pour $n\\geq3$,\n$$\\begin{align*}\n\\binom{n}{1}+\\binom{n}{2}+\\binom{n}{2}=5n&\\Leftrightarrow n+\\frac{n(n-1)}{2}+\\frac{n(n-1)(n-2)}{6}=5n\\\\\n &\\Leftrightarrow n(-24+3(n-1)+(n-1)(n-2))=0\\Leftrightarrow n^2-25=0\\\\\n &\\Leftrightarrow n=5.\n\\end{align*}$$",
        "html": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\geq3\\)</span>, <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\n\\binom{n}{1}+\\binom{n}{2}+\\binom{n}{2}=5n&amp;\\Leftrightarrow n+\\frac{n(n-1)}{2}+\\frac{n(n-1)(n-2)}{6}=5n\\\\\n &amp;\\Leftrightarrow n(-24+3(n-1)+(n-1)(n-2))=0\\Leftrightarrow n^2-25=0\\\\\n &amp;\\Leftrightarrow n=5.\n\\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
